Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:32.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after\NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves \Ncaught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:30.11,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Back to the Present!\NHordy Makes a Move!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Who shot our queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for the shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave no stone unturned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Tai! Queen Otohime! I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with this anger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! We found the shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Get to the rooftop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the shooter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a gun in his hand. There is no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei-san! We just killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Boss Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will ruin the Queen's efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be able to rest in peace like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, because he was a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if he was a pirate or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Hordy! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who killed our queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime was killed by a human!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't deserve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...killed the Queen who wanted \Nnothing but peaceful coexistence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and broke our hearts just when we were\N inspired by her words and about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...extend our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took our beloved one's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even by taking your life,\N Otohime-sama can never come back, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no justice in this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad! Unbelievably sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the King still in the Hard Shell Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear that? He's lost all control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't open it while I have \Nthis urge to kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-sama, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shooter had a gun in his hand so \None of our soldiers shot him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have killed him \Neven if he were unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Otohime would not allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know when this \Ncycle of revenge started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I kill somebody, I would \Nonly perpetuate that cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witnessing my actions would\N make children's eyes cold
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they would harbor \Nhatred and become bitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the cycle of revenge spiraling on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could relate to what Otohime was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as long as it was somebody else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why shouldn't I kill the man\N who shot my wife to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand that-jamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a soldier, I have taken many \Nlives in reprisal for my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed many humans who besieged us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I thought I have no place \Nhelping Otohime in what she was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I just stood by and watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should an innocent one like \Nher die and a man like me still live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take over her quest \Nbecause my hands are sullied
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by what I have done in the past-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But we all change and we all \Nare full of contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Fish-Men, and humans too. And there are \Nthings that only soldiers can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:13.25,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A FEW DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my own wife's funeral \N- I have to attend it-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama! Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to make you feel so left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Father-sama, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:01.63,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TO SHIRAHOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These letters keep flying in wherever I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are already 5 of them, Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a love letter! \NBut Shirahoshi is only 6 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:16.23,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'M IN LUV WITH YOU. I SUSPECT.\N MARRY ME. VANDER DECKEN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Vander Decken?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the name of a pirate family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My children won't attend the funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There could be an accomplice\N still lurking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And catch this pirate named Decken now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Prince Fukaboshi!\N--Prince-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens of the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I \Nwant to tell you all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please give me your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In her last moment, my mother said happily,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We are almost there at that\N place under the real sun."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have decided to take over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our mother's dream and dedicate\N our lives to seeing it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably are not going to be \Nready for the World Summit in 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there will be another one in \N6 years and another in 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this tragedy made you\N change your view of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will get rid of all the \Nsignatures that were left unburned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when your emotional\N wounds heal someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's dream about the sun together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the decade that followed, \Nnot just Fukaboshi, Ryuboshi and Manboshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also the King and the Princess spoke\N to the nation through the monitor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all while signatures kept mounting up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was how we have been fighting against\N discrimination for the last 16 years
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the beginning of the Fish-Man Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong, who did horrible \Nthings to your hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:15:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was like a brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he engaged in violence, we were willing to \Ngo anywhere in order to stop him ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he always paid off the \NNavy soldiers around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to keep his actions secret from the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, I made you \Nand many others suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you cut your own belly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay her with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still won't forgive you but it \Ncould relieve Nami-san of her pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nami-san, what they \Nhave done to you was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:16:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a different story!\N This man didn't mean to hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take any punishment!\N If it makes you happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. The only one I hate is Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm glad that you are not the \Nmastermind of the Arlong Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're Luffy's friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I've gone through \Nhell because of the Arlong Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I met my friends in \Nthat horrible turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One thing led to another\N and I am who I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna hate you \Nbecause you're a Fish-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't pity me because of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:17:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad because I'm \Nenjoying it in the present!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't matter who did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get angry on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the people \Non the island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the tragedy we endured \Nnor of our anger towards humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two grew up together and\N he's like a brother to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you couldn't just kill \Nhim even though you were justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve such words of kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I know how hard it is to be a big brother!\N You're the man, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Tiger and Otoshime \Nand everybody very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've been feeling so much pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! I thought it was \Nunusual for you to listen so quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Jimbei, are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? I am not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! I said I am not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... Oh, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Jimbei, what did happen to the \Nthief that Coward's mother caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been sleeping most of \Nthe time! That was the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Was it?\N--It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so your name is Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami-chin, she's the Princess!\N You can't say "Hey"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was crying remembering my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was quite a woman, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are Nami-chin-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mermaid Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chin is like her nickname.\N Her real name has no "chin."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:20:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I have known you since I was a \Nkid although we just met for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel comfortable with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Maybe that's because we've\N been through similar things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took too much time. I need to know \Nwho is still at the Ryugu Palace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy and his crew invaded the palace \Nand captured the King and his soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't know what \Nhappened to four of your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the information we have so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things are going as Hordy planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the whole country might be \Nin a terrible state by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what his plan is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspected he was up to something\N in the Fish-Man District
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after retiring from the army,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he never revealed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy hates humans more\N than Arlong-san did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has been living on the resentment and \Nanger of the Fish-Men, and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is something about him \Nclearly different from Arlong-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san would look down on humans \Nbut he would never hurt other Fish-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hordy will attack those Fish-Men\N who are sympathetic to humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year is the World Summit which\N takes place every four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they gathered enough signatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune will express his \Nintention to the world finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to relocate the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he is planning to block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he wants more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Video Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.46,0:22:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's projecting something on the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, everybody on the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.36,0:23:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain of the New Fish-Man \NPirates from the Fish-Man District,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy broadcasts his ambition \Nacross all of Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His shocking intention is \Nto destroy the Ryugu Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and establish himself as the new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens of Fish-Man Island \Nhad been deeply unsettled already,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Hordy's announcement has \Nfurther filled them with dread!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Kingdom in Shock! \NAn Order to Execute Neptune Issued!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
